[32m+[m[32m## 📋 Runtime Modes[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m### Demo Mode (`--mode demo`)[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Purpose**: Testing and development without external dependencies[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Features**:[m
[32m+[m[32m  - Mock environment with configurable random seed[m
[32m+[m[32m  - 3 drones and 4 victims by default[m
[32m+[m[32m  - Deterministic behavior for reproducible testing[m
[32m+[m[32m  - No external simulator required[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Use Cases**:[m
[32m+[m[32m  - Unit testing[m
[32m+[m[32m  - Algorithm development[m
[32m+[m[32m  - CI/CD pipelines[m
[32m+[m[32m  - Quick prototyping[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m### Sim Mode (`--mode sim`)[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Purpose**: Integration with AirSim for realistic simulation[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Features**:[m
[32m+[m[32m  - Connects to AirSim simulator via TCP[m
[32m+[m[32m  - Uses structured data contracts for telemetry and commands[m
[32m+[m[32m  - Lazy imports (AirSim dependencies only loaded when needed)[m
[32m+[m[32m  - Clear error messages if AirSim is unavailable[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Requirements**:[m
[32m+[m[32m  - AirSim simulator running[m
[32m+[m[32m  - AirSim Python client installed[m
[32m+[m[32m  - Network connectivity to simulator host[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Use Cases**:[m
[32m+[m[32m  - Hardware-in-the-loop testing[m
[32m+[m[32m  - Realistic mission simulations[m
[32m+[m[32m  - Sensor data processing validation[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m### Dashboard Mode[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Purpose**: Real-time monitoring and control[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Features**:[m
[32m+[m[32m  - Web-based interface (Streamlit)[m
[32m+[m[32m  - Real-time fleet status visualization[m
[32m+[m[32m  - Mission tracking and control[m
[32m+[m[32m  - Triage priority display[m
[32m+[m[32m  - Auto-refresh capabilities[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Access**: http://localhost:8501[m
