[32m+[m[32m- [x] **Demo Mode**: Fully functional and tested[m
[32m+[m[32m- [x] **Sim Mode**: Activation path ready (requires AirSim installation)[m
[32m+[m[32m- [x] **Dashboard**: Real-time monitoring available[m
[32m+[m[32m- [x] **Logging**: Configurable logging with multiple levels[m
[32m+[m[32m- [x] **Configuration**: Multiple configuration sources with priority ordering[m
[32m+[m[32m- [x] **Error Handling**: Clear error messages and graceful degradation[m
[32m+[m[32m- [ ] **AirSim Client**: Requires external AirSim Python package installation[m
[32m+[m[32m- [ ] **Performance Metrics**: Basic metrics available; advanced monitoring needed[m
[32m+[m[32m- [ ] **Deployment**: Manual deployment; containerization recommended for production[m
